{"tid":51684,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[真事]今日去戲院買飛,比前面條友嚇親","createTime":"2016-12-23T12:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T12:24:02.000Z","uid":9564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4da9f61b262aa33ecaf01bfee9da91ac8711e8","tid":51684,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日趁得閒想買場優先場既戲，係咩戲就唔方便講la<br />\n不過差唔多排到我果時,前面個客,4 50歲度,買左好耐都未買到,咁我聽下咩事,點知聽落比佢嚇死<br />\n<br />\n客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 票房職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我話睇夜晚7點半 SS in quit呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sorry?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> SS in quit喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思先生,我地好似無呢套戲喎<br />\n<br />\n之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />指住頭頂果啲seatplan銀幕,然後好大聲咁話: 咩無呀,上面都寫住7點半,SS in quit,刺客教條,仲有幾排位喺度,點樣無先?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哦&hellip;哦,好明白,7點半既刺客教條,數字請揀位,銀幕喺你呢邊&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n跟住成個票房啲人靜晒，我忍得好辛苦，而票房職員繼續保持鎮靜,處理埋呢個客先<br />\n<br />\n至於我就已經喺隔離櫃台買好飛急急腳走先,費事笑出聲盞尷尬la&hellip;"},{"pid":"f06ab8512f5e1557ec84a569ae2f78f3fd9341e0","tid":51684,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:09:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93ad96fef0ed061aac16dfff08521e16b64a5041","tid":51684,"uid":66490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"SS in quit？ 佢點讀到咁"},{"pid":"0af32d3e086cd77afc16141b217fbd455cb2f13d","tid":51684,"uid":28256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SS in quit？ 佢點讀到咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n ass ass in creed <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma